cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.NE, cs.DS

The paper proposes a new approach for time series modeling using graph neural networks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of a graph structure to represent the evolutionary relations among intrinsic factors of time series data suggests that it may also fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The use of recurrent neural networks in the proposed method suggests that it may also fall under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the use of real-world datasets and time series classification tasks suggests that it may also fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
